title: Scheduled Maintenance - Patch 5.12 - 25/06/2015
body:
Summoners,

Patch 5.12 is happening tomorrow and we want to make sure everyone is ready!

On 25/06/2015, starting at 02:30 AM AEDT, ranked queues will be disabled in preparation for patch 5.12. At 04:00 AM AEDT, the servers will be shut down and all games currently in progress will end in a draw and stats will not be recorded. We estimate the battlegrounds will be unavailable for 6 hours.

As always, keep an eye on the [Server Status Page](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#oce) for the most up-to-date information.

Cheers,
-Mindstar

replies.body: I've high ping problems (around 250) since yesterday. The first day of 5.12, I can't play any games now even Co-Op. Please help Riot...
Has diamond 5 clamping been fixed with this patch for oce?
AEDT? i thought we were AEST now.

You are right!  That was a mistake - thanks for pointing it out :)

Cheers
Mindstar
